title: Microsoft persuades ASUS to install Office on its Android phones
text:
Microsoft persuades ASUS to install Office on its Android phones 
Published By: Tuaw.com - Today 
ASUS will install Office apps and other "innovative product solutions" from Microsoft on its Android phones thanks to a new patent licensing...
